  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when it was time to convince us that we're not leaving to concentration camps to be slaughtered-- as the rumors were then becoming very, very, very vivid and very clear-- he told the women, and he told the professional men, and he told everybody, on the marktplatz, that we're going-- this is as the Russians were beginning to invade the fronts of the other side of Poland-- that they wanted us to-- that they're taking us to Germany, and they're going to-- they have wonderful places for us to work in.",
      "word_count": 92
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we're going to work for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it's going to be wonderful conditions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that the women should bring their pots and sewing utensils and all the things that you need to run a household, and the-- because these things were very scarce in Germany, due to the war.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they told musicians to bring their instruments, the [NON-ENGLISH], the shoemakers, to bring their tools, and everyone should pack and bring everything they can, because these things are not available and so they have them to go to work.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he described a perfect utopia for where we were going to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he apparently got away with it, though he at least-- I suppose under certain conditions, you'll listen to any story, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the elders listened to the story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And maybe the people in Warsaw didn't want to listen to that story because they were already-- their minds were made up that this story isn't going to fly.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, I suppose, where there's hope, where there is some sort of an inkling of some hope, you will listen to anything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so consequently, everybody started packing, and, and whether you believed them or not, you wanted to believe it.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
